<i>noun</i>: 월급날 [월금날], 봉급날 [봉ː금날] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>월급날 [월금날]</dt><br>
<dd>payday; salary day</dd><br>
<dd>일한 대가로 한 달마다 지급하는 보수를 받는 날.</dd><br>
<dd>The day when one gets paid for one's labor on a monthly basis.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>봉급날 [봉ː금날]</dt><br>
<dd>payday</dd><br>
<dd>봉급을 받는 날.</dd><br>
<dd>The day on which salaries are paid.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>